extends layout

block content
  div.welcome
    h1 Welcome to Cabrini-Green Devops!!
    p Why should you think about making a career switch to work in tech? Watch the video below to find out
    p
      iframe(width="1120",height="630",src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jw98oh8HF5o",title="YouTube video player",frameborder="0",allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture",allowfullscreen)
    p Many people want to work in tech but getting there is not easy. Companies expect you to already have a lot of skills before they will be willing to invest in hiring you and continuing to train you. This school will help you get the skills you need to qualify for many tech jobs.
    p Let's talk about two types of tech jobs: developers and operations.
      ul
        li Developer jobs tend to focus on building products for people to use e.g. YouTube.
        li Operations jobs tend to focus on providing a platform for the application to run securely and reliably.
      span Devops jobs include elements of both of those two roles. Devops engineers build software to help the operations and development teams work well together. Watch the video below to learn more
    p
      iframe(width="1120",height="630",src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6IfRG80KRIY",title="YouTube video player",frameborder="0", allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen)

    h2 Want to get started?
    p Checkout the&nbsp;
      a(href="/roadmap") roadmap&nbsp;
      span to read more about what you will be learning?

